Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.46,0:00:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真咲  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我有想和你说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,时宗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,灭掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,水  拿水来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没事了  已经…不烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为了不蔓延开来而设计好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,设计好的?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是说有人做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静一点  我很意外地你居然胆子这么小
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,别笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,话说那孩子呢  小爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,处刑  一定要处刑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,处刑…处刑…处刑…处刑…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,帮忙倒酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这次也拜托你了  因为你最会写了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:03:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,住持也真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,买了高价的法号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,却让不相关的人写给他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这种程度的小佛这就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,趁没忘记的时候  这是这个月的份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…关于此有些话想跟你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要谈的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你就先发发慈悲…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:22.54,Comment,,0,0,0,,等一下  还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,慈悲…慈悲…慈悲…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,开门  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你少蹬鼻子上脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能帮你把以前的债都还清
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这钱足够了吧  受够你们母女俩生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0F0B09&\bord0\shad0\pos(182,338)\frz51.66}贱和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0F0B09&\bord0\shad0\pos(449,532)\frz36.4}去\N死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你个该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你个该死的  你个该死的  下地狱去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,处刑  处刑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,处刑…处刑…处刑…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪里  那家伙到底在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,出现…什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喵太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,吩咐你的给我好好做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙连偷东西都不会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,把书包还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以叫你赶快照我说的去做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,算了  这家伙真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,射偏的话  或许会打到蜂巢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不要  不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,处刑…处刑…处刑…处刑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,给我  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那种人  不能再让他进家门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪你惹怒他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我的错?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再依靠了  那种人的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法啊  那个人  只留下债款就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,想想办法啊  想想办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:10:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,处刑…处刑…处刑…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喵太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,今天已经是两天没吃饭了  不要把饭当食物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fade(420,0)\c&HE6DFDB&\bord0\shad3\4c&H332721&\move(1326,113,-250,113)}我们支持你~~~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fade(420,0)\c&HE6DFDB&\bord0\shad3\4c&H332721&\move(1360,310,-750,310)}目标  游骑兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\c&HE6DFDB&\bord0\shad3\4c&H332721&\move(1410,380,390,380)}这货傻子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\c&HE6DFDB&\bord0\shad3\4c&H332721&\move(1426,520,330,520)}夏井◯川◯记录?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,游骑兵五训之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是蛇还是青蛙  为了成为真正的游骑兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,能吃的我都会吃了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我孤独的训练就此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,玩耍的时间到此为止  下周我就要入伍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\c&HE6DFDB&\bord0\shad3\4c&H332721&\move(1500,300,-300,300)}哦吼、真的要入伍啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\c&HF6F7F5&\bord0\shad3\4c&H332721&\move(1450,420,650,420)}考试加油啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,朝着真正的游骑兵前进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,为了能在名为「人生」的生存游戏中存活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,大家  谢谢你们的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranger
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\c&HE6DFDB&\bord0\shad3\4c&H332721&\move(1330,230,-50,230)\b0}傻w子w
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\c&HE6DFDB&\bord0\shad3\4c&H332721&\move(1730,150,520,150)\b0}wwwwwRangerwwwww
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\c&HE6DFDB&\bord0\shad3\4c&H332721&\pos(530,150)\b0}wwwwwRangerwwwww
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\c&HE6DFDB&\bord0\shad3\4c&H332721&\move(1500,360,-180,360)\b0}Rangerwwwwww
